	   <tr><td colspan=2>When Siver spawns, she is not targetable. However, the green light you saw would have been accompanied by a message in your chat window (provided you are close enough to the action) saying, &quot;A whisperling begins to cast a spell.&quot;<br><br>The light under the rock let's people who are aware of her to know she is there for you to say &quot;Lumanes.&quot; But to those who have not yet discovered the quest, the spell effect and casting message gives them the clue that there is something more to the rock than originally meets the eye. ;)<br>&nbsp;<br>Garanth Ealdwulf<br>Povar</td></tr>
